# Thermod Changelog

 - 1.0.0: first stable release
 
 - 1.1.0:
     o move the averaging-task outside PiAnalogZeroThermometer in order to use
       that feature with any thermometer
     o add a "similarity-checker" for thermometers in order to recognize
       malfunctions that produce an abnormal temperature reading

 - 1.2.0:
    o Add support for cooling system
    o Add support for 1-Wire thermometers
    o Add filter and jail files for fail2ban
    o Add a degree scale adapter (now the temperatures can be shown in
      fahrenheit degrees even if the thermometers are in celsius)
